Invocation Name: cook a duck
des:
Cook a Duck provides quick and common ways of cooking a duck.

To start, just say "Alexa, launch Cook a Duck" or "Alexa, open Cook a Duck" to get the instruction on cooking a duck.

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
